item.title: The Last of Us Season 2, Episode 7: "Convergence"
item.description:
Spencer and Lee review the final episode of season 2 of HBO's "The Last of Us." They start with a general discussion about the state of TV, and specifically big budget, fantasy TV. Then, in a throw back episode, Lee leads the line-by-line recap. They end with Best Line of the Episode, Winners/ Losers and Therapy Time with Lee.

Let us know what show you'd like us to cover next! facebook.com/mangumtalks or mangumtalkspodcasts@gmail.com
